Events that occurred on 15 July.
==On Earth==
</noinclude>
* '''[[1883]]''' - [[Inklings|Inkling]] [[Adam Fox]] is born. 
* '''[[1915]]''' - [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] becomes a second lieutenant, and is appointed to the 13th Service Battalion of the Lancashire Fusiliers.
* '''[[1919]]''' - Tolkien is officially released from service, well over a year after the [[World War I|war]]'s end.
* '''[[1955]]''' - [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] writes [[Letter 165b]].
* '''[[1964]]''' - [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] sends [[Letter to Miss J.L. Curry|a letter to Miss J.L. Curry]].
* '''[[1979]]''' - [[Mythcon 10]] in [[wikipedia:San Jose, California|San Jose, California]].
* '''[[1998]]''' - [[Mythcon 29]] in [[wikipedia:Wheaton, Illinois|Wheaton, Illinois]].
* '''[[2004]]''' - [[The Lord of the Rings Symphony]] in [[wikipedia:Seattle|Seattle]].
* '''[[2004]]''' - [[Tolkien Thing|Tolkien Thing VI]] in [[wikipedia:Hohenahr|Hohensolms, Hohenahr]], [[wikipedia:Germany|Germany]].
* '''[[2006]]''' - [[Tolkien Thing|Tolkien Thing VIII]] in [[wikipedia:Diez, Germany|Diez]], [[wikipedia:Germany|Germany]].
* '''[[2007]]''' - [[Tolkien Thing|Tolkien Thing IX]] in [[wikipedia:Diez, Germany|Diez]], [[wikipedia:Germany|Germany]].
* '''[[2010]]''' - [[Tolkien Thing]] 2010 in [[wikipedia:Bad Hersfeld|Bad Hersfeld]], [[wikipedia:Germany|Germany]].
* '''[[2011]]''' - [[Tolkien Thing]] 2011 in [[wikipedia:Breuberg|Breuberg]], [[wikipedia:Germany|Germany]].
* '''[[2011]]''' - [[Mythcon 42]] in [[wikipedia:Albuquerque, New Mexico|Albuquerque, New Mexico]].
* '''[[2013]]''' - [[Mythcon 44]] at [[wikipedia:Michigan State University|Michigan State University]], [[wikipedia:East Lansing, Michigan|East Lansing]].
